                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;10967  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;10968  void watchdog_enable (void) 
009c76  495a              LDR      r1,|L2.40416|
;;;10969  {
;;;10970  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;
009c78  05c8              LSLS     r0,r1,#23
009c7a  6041              STR      r1,[r0,#4]
;;;10971  LPC_WDT->WDCLKSEL=0;
009c7c  2100              MOVS     r1,#0
009c7e  6101              STR      r1,[r0,#0x10]
;;;10972  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;
009c80  2103              MOVS     r1,#3
009c82  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;10973  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009c84  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
009c86  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10974  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
009c88  2155              MOVS     r1,#0x55
009c8a  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10975  }
009c8c  4770              BX       lr
;;;10976  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;10977  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;10978  void watchdog_reset (void) 
009c8e  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
;;;10979  {
;;;10980  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009c90  0748              LSLS     r0,r1,#29
009c92  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10981  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
009c94  2155              MOVS     r1,#0x55
009c96  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10982  }
009c98  4770              BX       lr
;;;10983  
                          ENDP

                  SysTick_Handler PROC
;;;10989  //***********************************************
;;;10990  void SysTick_Handler (void) 	 /* SysTick Interrupt Handler (1ms)    */

;;;10991  {
;;;10992  //sys_plazma++;
;;;10993  b2000Hz=1;

;;;10996  	{
;;;10997  	LPC_GPIO1->FIODIR|=(1UL<<26);

;;;10998  	LPC_GPIO1->FIOPIN^=(1UL<<26);

009cba  6341              STR      r1,[r0,#0x34]
                  |L2.40124|
;;;10999  	}
;;;11000  
;;;11001  if(++t0cnt4>=2)

009cc0  1c49              ADDS     r1,r1,#1

;;;11003  t0cnt4=0;

;;;11004  b1000Hz=1;

;;;11005  
;;;11006  	bFF=(char)(GET_REG(LPC_GPIO0->FIOPIN, 27, 1));

;;;11007  	if(bFF!=bFF_) hz_out++;

                  |L2.40174|
;;;11008  	bFF_=bFF;
